annotationDatas.title: Head of radius
annotationDatas.content: Articulates with the capitulum of the humerus

annotationDatas.title: Radial tuberosity
annotationDatas.content: The site of insertion of the rendon of the biceps brachii.

annotationDatas.title: Nutrient foramen
annotationDatas.content: A tunnel through the cortex of the bone. Creates an entrance for a nutrient artery to supply the bone.

annotationDatas.title: Styloid process
annotationDatas.content: The insertion point of the brachioradialis tendon and the origin of the radical collateral ligament.

annotationDatas.title: Dorsal tubercle
annotationDatas.content: Also known as Lister's tubercle. Acts as a pulley for the tendon of Extensor Pollicis Longus.

annotationDatas.title: Ulnar notch
annotationDatas.content: The site of articulation with the distal ulna.
